Ng%C3%B4n-S%E1%BB%AD/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%A7-t%E1%BA%A1p-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-bpMUMZJY00xbrJ28xKsCww">Nhạc phủ tạp từ kỳ 2 - 樂府雜詞其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Ng%C3%B4n-S%E1%BB%AD/author-7fyND8bmUCc7qgGU5ulZkg">Lưu Ngôn Sử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-C%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Ph%C3%BA-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-nh%E1%BA%ADp-giai-v%C5%A9/poem-sUripu8vBhBZNrYNCPUb4Q">Phú đắc nhập giai vũ - 賦得入階雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-C%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-vVug93Sf3-jdm37KhWEtiw">Tiêu Cương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/S%E1%BB%A9-h%E1%BB%93i-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-s%C6%A1n-gia/poem-nB2_9F9-3Do3SWnJKboYvg">Sứ hồi đề sơn gia - 使回題山家</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C3%8Dch/Tr%C3%BAc-song-v%C4%83n-phong-k%C3%BD-Mi%C3%AAu-Ph%C3%A1t-T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%B1/poem-a9o70FfLlaUx8kVu4YHKQA">Trúc song văn phong ký Miêu Phát, Tư Không Thự - 竹窗聞風寄苗發司空曙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C3%8Dch/author-WesEXQEj_Uo-QKdZcJ784w">Lý Ích</a>)<br></div>	</div>
